Company Profile:Singex Exhibitions is a wholly owned entity of Singex Holdings, a meeting, incentive, convention and exhibition (MICE) veteran with over 30 years of industry expertise.  A wholly owned subsidiary of Temasek Holdings - one of the largest investment holding companies in Singapore - Singex is focused on creating international market platforms through professional conference, exhibition and venue management.Whether it is an event launch, an adaptation of a successful overseas tradeshow, or a re-launch of an existing business event, Singex Exhibitions has the expertise to assist from event conceptualisation and planning, creative execution and marketing, to on-site operation and logistics support.We combine our experience with industry know-how to maintain the integrity of our clients’ brand across various event platforms.
Job Description:Currently we are looking for Marketing Assistants to support Marketing Manager with the marketing and promotion of events. Duties include data research (desk & phone research), building partnerships with associations and media, website content management.We're looking for candidates who are confident on the phone, responsible and accountable.
Please apply for this position by submitting your text CV using InternSG.
